{"title":"阿富汗的谚语和俚语","authors":["张光启"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":2,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿富汗的谚语和俚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在自己街上劣犬也变成了老虎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驴子不能因为打它而变成马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少说话，多做事才是男子汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人——比石头还坚硬，比花还温柔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水不能用刀斧砍开，水和火不能结合起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的玉米饼要比别人的抓饭香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一千个朋友还嫌少，一个敌人够多了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张光启辑译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}